    <string name="privacy_title">Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_body" formatted="false">OpenSleep is 100% committed to your privacy.

• 100% On-Device Processing: Phone motion sensors and microphone-derived sound-level features are analyzed completely locally. Raw audio is not stored, and no personal telemetry leaves your device.
• Local AI Model: The sleep assistant runs a fully local Gemma 4 LLM entirely on-device (zero servers, no external APIs).
• Open Source: OpenSleep is a fully transparent, open-source project. You can inspect the source code anytime.
• Health Sync: Sleep sessions are stored locally and synced directly with Google Health Connect.
• Support: If you have any questions or feedback, contact us at timmy@opensleep.tech.</string>
